flavor_text_entries.gold:
This upgraded
version of PORYGON
is designed for space exploration.
It can't fly,
though.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Further research
enhanced its abil­
ities. Sometimes, it may exhibit
motions that were
not programmed.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
This manmade
POKéMON evolved
from the latest technology. It
may have unprog­
rammed reactions.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
PORYGON2 was created by humans using
the power of science. The man-made
POKéMON has been endowed with artificial intelligence that enables it
to learn new gestures and emotions
on its own.

flavor_text_entries.leafgreen:

designed for space exploration. However,
it can’t even fly.
flavor_text_entries.diamond:

software installed, it became
capable of working in space.

flavor_text_entries.omega-ruby:
Porygon2 was created by humans using the power of science.
The man-made Pokémon has been endowed with artificial
intelligence that enables it to learn new gestures and emotions
on its own.
flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
Porygon2 was created by humans using the power of science.
The man-made Pokémon has been endowed with artificial
intelligence that enables it to learn new gestures and emotions
on its own.
flavor_text_entries.sun:
For the purposes of planetary development,
Porygon was updated with the most
cutting-edge technology available.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
Porygon was updated to a new version in
readiness for planetary development. But that
dream remains unrealized as yet.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
AI has been installed in it. It learns various
things all on its own, but it even remembers
things it doesn’t need to know.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
Even though it doesn’t die in the vacuum of
space, it can’t move around very well in
zero gravity.
flavor_text_entries.sword:
This is a Porygon that was updated with special
data. Porygon2 develops itself by learning about
many different subjects all on its own.
flavor_text_entries.shield:
After artificial intelligence was implemented in
Porygon2, the Pokémon began using a strange
language that only other Porygon2 understand.
flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
A bizarre item caused this Pokémon to evolve. While it now
exhibits many new gestures and expressions, its biology
remains inscrutable.
